    *   `public FragmentPayDiscountBinding c;`: An instance of a generated ViewBinding class, `FragmentPayDiscountBinding`, which provides type-safe, direct references to the UI elements defined in its corresponding layout XML.
    *   `public PaymentDiscountTypeSelectAdapter d;`: An adapter object, suggesting it populates a list (likely a `RecyclerView`) with different payment discount types for user selection.
    *   `public CouponBean e;`: A data structure (bean) that will hold information about the selected or applied coupon. Its contents are crucial to the financial logic.
